title: Just your average ARAM game.
body:
https://imgur.com/ENgjNn4
Nothing unusual here, we lost by the way.

Can something be done about this?
Everyone getting +150 damage on their next auto in ten minutes or less is oppressive.

replies.body: I played ARAM several times on new account with at least one bot on each side. It is very positive gaming experience.

I never see people do this at my ARAM ELO.. nobody uses it except me.

7K damage with it in 25 minutes is funny, though.
